description:
On this episode of ANN International, learn about the Adventist Church’s Digital Evangelism Initiative and how the team is working toward spreading hope online.

Listen to the story of a woman whose life is transformed by Christ after the tragic loss of her daughter.

Discover how an ADRA Serbia bus meets the needs of local unhoused individuals in the region. 

Also, watch as a doctor finds her calling in caring for people in the Amazon rainforest. 

Stay tuned as ANN brings you these captivating stories and provides coverage of other global news. For a deeper dive into these headlines, visit adventist.news.

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
